#solar panel
efficiency ~20%
power output ~0.5 kW
area ~2 m^2, 72 silicon cells

#dam
China
- Three Gorges Dam: Yangtze River, 22 GW, gravity dam
- Baihetan Dam: Jinsha River, 16 GW
- Xiluodu Dam: Jinsha River, 14 GW, arch dam
- Wudongde Dam: Jinsha River, 10 GW
- Jinping-I Dam: arch dam
South America
- Itaipu Dam: Brazil/Paraguay, Paraná River, 14 GW
- Belo Monte Dam: Brazil, Xingu River, 11 GW
- Guri Dam: Venezuela, 10 GW, gravity/embankment dam
- Tucuruí Dam: Brazil, Tocantins River, 8 GW, gravity dam
- Ilha Solteira Dam: Brazil, Paraná River, embankment dam
- Yacyretá Dam: Argentina/Paraguay, Paraná River
- Salto Grande Dam: Argentina/Uruguay, Uruguay River
North America
- Grand Coulee Dam: USA, Columbia River, Roosevelt Lake, gravity dam
- Daniel-Johnson Dam: Canada, Lake Manicouagan (impact crater), buttress dam
- Hoover Dam: USA, Colorado River, Lake Mead, arch-gravity dam
Russia
- Sayano-Shushenskaya Dam: Yenisey River, arch-gravity dam
- Krasnoyarsk Dam: Yenisey River
- Bratsk Dam: Angara River
- Ust Ilimskaya: Angara River
- Chirkey Dam: arch dam
India
- Tarbela Dam: Pakistan, Indus River, embankment dam
- Tehri Dam: India, embankment dam
- Koyna Dam: India
- Srisailam Dam: India, Krishna
Asia
